  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive enemies attack as long as possible in the world of <strong>Echo Storm</strong>! Use possibility to combine characters, weapons and abilities to become more powerful. Death resets the progress, but the longer you survive, the more abilities your character gets. Onslaught of enemies is growing too and the intensity of the battle is increasing. Find best abilities combination and try to destroy all enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/fea92a735075695e702871aeecbd33b8.poster.avif?t=1767825023\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/fea92a735075695e702871aeecbd33b8.webm?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/fea92a735075695e702871aeecbd33b8.mp4?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the world of Echo Storm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose</strong> start <strong>character,</strong> <strong>weapon</strong> <strong>and ability</strong> which better fit <strong>your</strong> game <strong>style</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find more efficient ways to eliminate specific enemies and ways to evade their attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive on the <strong>5 different planets</strong> with a various aggressive creatures and conditions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combine abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You receive a new ability every time when your level increases. <strong>Make unique combinations</strong> to get more powerful!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/c4c8d4d1860614632fff28a09d6d7577.avif?t=1767825023\" width=598 height=292 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrades</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new characters, weapons and abilities to get a lot of new ways to survive in the world of <strong>Echo Storm</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your base to improve character health, damage and other stats, and receive more resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get into fight now!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/7862357d58b12ef074e835fe40e87840.poster.avif?t=1767825023\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/7862357d58b12ef074e835fe40e87840.webm?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/7862357d58b12ef074e835fe40e87840.mp4?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive enemies attack as long as possible in the world of <strong>Echo Storm</strong>! Use possibility to combine characters, weapons and abilities to become more powerful. Death resets the progress, but the longer you survive, the more abilities your character gets. Onslaught of enemies is growing too and the intensity of the battle is increasing. Find best abilities combination and try to destroy all enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/fea92a735075695e702871aeecbd33b8.poster.avif?t=1767825023\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/fea92a735075695e702871aeecbd33b8.webm?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/fea92a735075695e702871aeecbd33b8.mp4?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the world of Echo Storm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose</strong> start <strong>character,</strong> <strong>weapon</strong> <strong>and ability</strong> which better fit <strong>your</strong> game <strong>style</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find more efficient ways to eliminate specific enemies and ways to evade their attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive on the <strong>5 different planets</strong> with a various aggressive creatures and conditions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combine abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You receive a new ability every time when your level increases. <strong>Make unique combinations</strong> to get more powerful!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/c4c8d4d1860614632fff28a09d6d7577.avif?t=1767825023\" width=598 height=292 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrades</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new characters, weapons and abilities to get a lot of new ways to survive in the world of <strong>Echo Storm</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your base to improve character health, damage and other stats, and receive more resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get into fight now!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/7862357d58b12ef074e835fe40e87840.poster.avif?t=1767825023\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/7862357d58b12ef074e835fe40e87840.webm?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/7862357d58b12ef074e835fe40e87840.mp4?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
